358
00:42:27,679 --> 00:42:30,059
[SPEAKER_01] To je sad jedan težak proces u kojem ti, ono,

359
00:42:30,079 --> 00:42:34,079
[SPEAKER_01] pričali smo već o tome, stvoriš jedno, ono, stvarala si biznis, stvarala si bebu,

360
00:42:34,079 --> 00:42:35,400
[SPEAKER_01] ti si unjela sve u to.

361
00:42:35,400 --> 00:42:37,880
[SPEAKER_01] I sad možda ti nećeš osjetiti slastog.

362
00:42:37,880 --> 00:42:41,880
[SPEAKER_01] Kada se otarasimo toga, to je jedan težak proces,

363
00:42:41,880 --> 00:42:45,139
